    <title>Nintendo is making an alarm clock so you can wake up to Zelda and Super Mario sounds</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A photo of Nintendo’s Alarmo alarm clock." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4AhMmGzoz-5eWsCzABH5xvkukg8=/0x1:3500x2334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73641941/NSC_Alarmo_6.0.jpg" /&gt;
